Title: Fallout Was A B-Tier Project
Description: I talk about how Fallout was never a high-status project at Interplay until very shortly before it shipped.

Title: The Gemini protocol seen by this HTTP client person
Description: There is again a pull-request submitted to the curl project to bring support for the Gemini protocol. It seems like a worthwhile effort that I support, even if it is also a lot of work involved and it might take some time before it reaches the state in which it can be merged. A previous attempt at doing this was abandoned a while ago.
